GetDetectors.documentation: Gets all of detectors. This is a paginated API. If you provide a null maxSizePerPage, this actions retrieves a maximum of 10 records per page. If you provide a maxSizePerPage, the value must be between 5 and 10. To get the next page results, provide the pagination token from the GetEventTypesResponse as part of your request. A null pagination token fetches the records from the beginning.

UpdateModelVersion.documentation:
Updates a model version. You can update the description and status attributes using this action. You can perform the following status updates:

  1. Change the TRAINING_COMPLETE status to ACTIVE
